# Logo Icon Regeneration

- Canonical source logo is `Resources/logo.png`.
- If `Resources/logo.png` is added, replaced, renamed, or edited, run:
  - `scripts/make_app_icon.sh`
- If the user asks to "update logo", "regenerate app icon", "run logo script", or equivalent, run:
  - `scripts/make_app_icon.sh`
- Run the command from project root: `cd /Users/calwest/Documents/Guardian && scripts/make_app_icon.sh`
- After running, confirm the generated outputs exist:
  - `build/icons/AppIcon.iconset`
  - `build/icons/AppIcon.icns`
- If the script fails, report the error and fix the script or input assumptions before finishing.
